cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.HC 

The paper deals with video summarization, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of region cues and learning a regressor to predict importance is a machine learning approach, which falls under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with wearable cameras and the interaction of the camera wearer with objects and people, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
